lines.text: Prague Chocolate is a Czech family company. The company manufactures and sells
quality chocolate products. The most popular are dry roasted almonds in chocolate
with different flavours (cinnamon, ginger, chili and salt) and the , Mandala" collection.
Prague Chocolate is also well known for its original hot chocolate!
The company opened its own chocolate Cafe & Bistro in 2015 where you are now
sitting. All food and drinks are prepared with love and joy directly in our kitchen. We
mostly use fresh quality ingredients especially from Czech farmers and from local
sources. We prefer food without chemical treatment or in organic form.
Hot meals are served from 12:00 AM to 19:00 PM.
Spring in our kitchen is welcomed by fresh herbs, young farm cheeses
and colorful salads! We also prepared special smoothies to strengthen
and detoxify the body after the long winter.

Hot Chocolate with Fresh Fruit Pecommended!!
Our harmonized water tastes so much better than the tap version. Water on its
way through the water supply flows through many valves and treatment plants
under unnaturally high pressure. It therefore loses its natural vital and biological
value. Thanks to our harmonizing mandala and precious stones it regains its
original quality and taste. Try it for yourself.

Wines are specific by natural production process with minimal intervention.
No additives are added during the process, the wine ferments spontaneously.
Grapes come from organic or biodynamic vineyards. Wines therefore excel
in their natural character and perfectly reflect the terroir from where they
come from. Wines complement our specialties - cheese platter and first class
Prosecco, Ca'Di Rajo, Brut DOC - dry, made by charmat method, Italy, Treviso
Dobra vinice, Cuvee Narodni Park 2016, white - dry, cuvee (Muller Thurgau,
Welschriesling, Rheinriesling), aged in kvevri for 7 months, Znojmo region
